### SafeVault API and Web Routes
### Base URL for local testing: http://localhost:5000 or https://localhost:5001

### ==============================================================================
### AUTHENTICATION API ROUTES (JWT)
### ==============================================================================

### Register new user via API
POST http://localhost:5123/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testuser@example.com",
  "password": "TestPassword123"
}

###

### Login to get JWT token
POST http://localhost:5123/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testuser@example.com",
  "password": "TestPassword123"
}

###

### Validate JWT token (requires Authorization header)
GET http://localhost:5123/api/auth/validate
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..On1jiEASAvS_mgbtn7SHFDkzjeM72OAp6qtJg3rdFzU

###

### Get current user info (requires valid JWT token)
GET http://localhost:5123/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..On1jiEASAvS_mgbtn7SHFDkzjeM72OAp6qtJg3rdFzU

###

