### ==============================================================================
### WORKFLOW EXAMPLES
### ==============================================================================

### Example 1: Complete API Authentication Flow
### 1. Register: POST /api/auth/register
### 2. Get token from response
### 3. Use token in subsequent requests: Authorization: Bearer {token}
### 4. Validate token: GET /api/auth/validate
### 5. Get user info: GET /api/auth/me

### Example 2: Web Form Authentication Flow
### 1. GET /Identity/Account/Register
### 2. POST /Identity/Account/Register (creates user)
### 3. Automatically logged in, cookie stored
### 4. Can now access protected pages
### 5. POST /Identity/Account/Logout to clear session
